Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.59,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:13.20,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,29th Suimei High School Culture Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.90,Sign,FLIER,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate Banana
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:24.92,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:37.49,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,That looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:41.03,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You're really getting the \Nhang of this, Sora—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:46.44,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the eyes of a fish \Nthat's been rotting in the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:47.39,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:50.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon's not finished yet, \Nso I've been pulling all-nighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:51.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:53.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have a quota to meet at \Nthe chocolate banana café, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:55.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:58.41,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You... You should have a banana, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:00.65,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,They're really nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.19,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:04.56,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:07.75,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't stare like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.65,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... you look great. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.78,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Really great! Doesn't she, Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just great...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:15.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:18.64,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's operating on autopilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:24.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard enough for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:26.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to Nyapollon's prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to \Ndo on Nyapollon right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so at least let me help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:45.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You could've at least told \Nme it looked good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:47.96,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:50.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Bring us a ton of customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make loads of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:59.01,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}#11 Milky Way Cat, Nyapollon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.90,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:13.50,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just shut \Ndown all culture festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.87,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,where I don't get to run around with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:18.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, you were that excited about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Haunted houses? Crêpes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful little blind spots...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.83,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,appear all over the school \Nduring a culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:30.92,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.99,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,some really thrilling "play" becomes possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:41.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've never experienced anything \Nmore thrilling than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:44.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Four days until opening, \Nand I've got even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.18,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,blocking to do \Nfor the drama sequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.20,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Nyapollon Production Schedule{\b0}\NFour days until opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's so thrilling, I wish \NI could just pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.27,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Opening!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.99,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same way, but the demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who won't allow that \Nis about to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,No one's sleeping on \Nthe job in here, are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.57,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Drink before you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.21,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a potion to restore \Nyour hit points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It says it'll guide \Nus beyond our limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.67,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it's still too \Nearly to exceed our limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.33,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's wake ourselves up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with something eye-opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:18.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron's wearing a cat girl \Nsuit for this year's art exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:22.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like she's a \Nmonster, but that's not right, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cat version of a \N"bunny girl" suit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Start building up your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:32.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron's so cute, it made my nose run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It gave you a nosebleed, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:37.48,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A cat girl, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.49,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it looks good on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Forest Exhibition, Etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:53.79,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Exhibition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Forest Exhibition, Etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:00.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the poster girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A forest exhibit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.10,Saku-main,ZEBRA,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.16,Saku-main,ZEBRA,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A café?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:22.61,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,According to Misaki, it combines \Nan exhibit, a café, caricatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.54,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the forest, omelet rice, and animal suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:28.23,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, "Forest Exhibition, Etc."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The "etc." carries too much weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This was handcrafted by \Na forest bear! Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:36.92,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll draw your face on \Nit in ketchup for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, kouhai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting me for this job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.34,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, who will it be? \NMe or Mashiron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing too close, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:49.97,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're never too close \Nnor too far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You draw the caricature right \Non the face? That's novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:58.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a rebel without a cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:02.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Senpai, but I choose Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.61,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I lost the battle between women!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.85,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. I have Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got such a delicate touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.41,Saku-main,RABBIT,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:17.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a caricature, \Nit's a portrait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's such a thing as cannibalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You did this out of spite, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you're finished eating, \Nlet's get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiron, your shift's \Nover too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's all go back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:41.88,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around. Let me see your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's got something wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing a cat's \Nskin over your birthday suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:56.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm wearing panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:00.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,As good as panties are, they aren't \Nthe solution to {\i1}every{\i0} problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.80,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.68,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Takoyaki, ikayaki, okonomiyaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:12.09,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I love Japanese culture festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:14.27,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so interested \Nin the culture festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.73,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you should have gone to \Nwork in the prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.69,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in my room, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:22.40,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Because you interest me even more \Nthan the culture festival, Ryunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.53,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd be willing to go with me—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:29.01,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,How could I go to a culture \Nfestival swarming with girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.57,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate women so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.45,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.66,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer, freeloader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.23,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't accentuate your \Ncleavage more than necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.19,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,This is my natural look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.30,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, stop looking up at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.06,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,First, you chide me for my fake smiles,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and now, you're rejecting \Nthe expression of my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:51.10,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that Japanese \Ngentlemen were bossy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:55.90,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling "bossy"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.52,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,You foreign insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.31,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I'll exterminate you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.10,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do it from there, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.99,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.59,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.64,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.40,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:18.33,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,This long interval bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.60,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Should we add a line?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.73,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You killed Nekosuke-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:26.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai, about this character...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.50,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you... Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:27.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:28.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:29.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:30.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This henchman. The little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to add some lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:39.39,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry. My brain isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Chin up, chin up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.44,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:41.90,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hustle, hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This Nekosuke character here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:58.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can do is cook dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:14.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Safe. Doesn't look like it'll stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've reached my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go wash my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This... is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:30.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:36.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:36.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:37.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! It wasn't on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you forgot to put up the sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.49,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,saying you were using the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I wasn't planning \Non taking my clothes off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose a kilogram when \Nyou took off your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's an urban legend \Nsaying you weigh less...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you stand on one leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.14,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.65,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,The flight departs on the \Nlast day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.77,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.73,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.24,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.35,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:27.31,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That was Mashiro's father in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.50,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro has people waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.62,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro will return to \Nwhere she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:53.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to take \Na look around the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:55.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:02.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You were drawing until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.87,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When it's just the two \Nof us, call me Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, is there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you're \Nnot telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.68,Saku-main,SHIHO,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.38,Saku-main,SHIHO,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, there's something I'd like \Nto ask you about the exhibit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:25.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. I'll be waiting in the prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:25.85,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.02,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro has people waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.57,Saku-thought,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro will return to \Nwhere she belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kanda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.98,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka, why are you dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.39,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,When I arrived at school, a salesgirl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.37,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with a ponytail forced me to wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but why a maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:56.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I promised him he could just \Nstand there if he did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:00.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd come \Nto the culture festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:01.89,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.05,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that woman \Ntook over my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.22,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting a lot of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We should be grateful to Rita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.12,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda, come check\N the climax with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.73,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the final battle \Nwith Ein the Hunchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.53,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,There are two synchronized \Ncontrols during the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.36,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The first is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.26,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge!\NEin's Cat Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.57,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,By lifting and lowering their hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the audience avoids Ein's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.62,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The second is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.77,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Once they're backed into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:34.80,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the audience has to clap their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.38,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout!!\NMeatball Beam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.38,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,The meatball beam shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Once it senses a set volume,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon will use her finishing move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.68,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be the one who revs \Nup the crowd, ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:55.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay. I'm kinda nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.11,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Kanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like there's \Nsomething missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.55,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:06.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Just having them \Nshout the name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:08.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of the attack feels like a \Nwaste of the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.63,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.88,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,We can manage to just barely \Nchange the program in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't have time to \Norder additional animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.96,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What's your idea to use \Nthe system effectively?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? No—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have an idea in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:26.68,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,A director has to be prepared \Nwhen he suggests a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.09,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:33.67,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,A director who loses his way just before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.54,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the development deadline \Nonly creates confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akasaka-kun, \Nyou're going too far again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:41.07,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time, \Nbut I guess there's no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.71,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You should really go think \Nabout your responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:48.12,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Special Lecture by Graduate Fujisawa Kazuki{\b0}\NFor Anyone Aiming to Become a Creator\NDiscussing the Future of Video Games
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fujisawa Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:53.33,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Lecturer: Graduate Fujisawa Kazuki
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:53.33,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,People often ask me how \Nto become a creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:57.21,Saku-main,KAZUki,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe the impulse or desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to create something comes from within...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and isn't something that can be taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.11,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,To create a product that appeals...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:08.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to the emotions of more users,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.00,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you must first move yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.95,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not move your own heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you cannot move the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.36,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Creating a product that \Nmoves your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:27.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.94,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon isn't what's in my heart right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.17,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.41,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:42.35,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke said you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.46,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Jin and Misaki are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They're waiting for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:53.21,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They're having an intimate moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:53.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.69,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Suimei High's culture festival is so lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:03.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time you told me \Nwhy you came to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.39,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:10.23,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you didn't answer me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:16.93,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing more than a \Nsubstitute for Misaki to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.53,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.75,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid to hurt Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:23.25,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You want to keep her by your side, \Npure and untouched, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.17,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you're with me instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.62,Saku-thought,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,At least think up a cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.71,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings for you were genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:46.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So were mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:48.99,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:52.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what "intimate" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:59.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? Jin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.62,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:04.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,She's my older sister and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.90,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.24,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:14.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.43,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we give it another shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.81,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,We've both grown \Nup a bit since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.53,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.78,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.76,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? I was joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:40.12,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If you answer me so seriously, \NI'm the one who'll be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.46,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.96,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Your jokes were never funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.07,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're going to college in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.30,Saku-main,FUUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:56.56,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, their literary department is \Nmore substantial than Suimei's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:17.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew, but I couldn't tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:23.83,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,He said he didn't want to give \N Fuuka-chan another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I always wondered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:31.26,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I figured Jin just hadn't\N gotten over Fuuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:37.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,But that means I have a \Nchance, too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:38.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.41,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I feel motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:42.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll make Nyapollon a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make this Jin's favorite memory, \Nand that goes for everyone else, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,M-Misaki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:52.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way, kouhai-kun, \Nwhat did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Was it about Fuuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:58.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That Jin-san was going \Nto college in Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.08,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, he did say \Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's your only reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get to see him every day anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:04.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:11.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, don't underestimate modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.07,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Osaka's only two and a half \Nhours away by bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.59,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's even faster by plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:19.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, do you have any concept \Nof time, space or money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter, as long as \Nyou really want to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about that irrepressible impulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:29.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to exceed our limits! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:36.32,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,380 kilometers with one grain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,memorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:46.76,Saku-main,SORTA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.97,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Nyapollon Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.97,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon, dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:58.68,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The timing for the switch \Nover to this 3D part...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.60,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean, \Nso don't get so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:13.99,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Making the best memory \Nwith Nyapollon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.77,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay if all \Nwe do is make memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.35,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to let Shiina \Ngo back to England?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.52,Saku-thought,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,In order to create a \Nproduct that appeals...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.41,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,to the emotions of more users,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:33.88,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,you must first move yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.14,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you really want to see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.05,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about that irrepressible impulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.93,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The impulse to move oneself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:47.85,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.85,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:53.36,Sign,MANGA,0000,0000,0000,,I...\NI want to stay at Nanohana Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.79,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,wrote her emotions into her manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:06.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the climax of Nyapollon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to add an impulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:20.43,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Emergency Sakura Hall Meeting!{\b0}\NI want to add an impulse to Milky Way Cat Nyapollon!!\Nby Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle between Nyapollon \Nand Ein the Hunchback.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The system measures the \Nvolume of the audience's cheers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.80,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and launches its special attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to use an additional value.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What value?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.73,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Carry on, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give Nyapollon \Nan energy gauge...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:38.04,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and empty it once before the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll have the audience \Nshout out the feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,they most want to convey to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They can shout whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if people declare their love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:50.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's fine if they just \Nmake a simple complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:53.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Their voices become energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and once the gauge is full,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.21,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Shout!!\NMeatball Beam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.92,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,it sets off the meatball beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.03,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:09.27,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Love will save the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does sound fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.77,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I can change the program in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.78,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.24,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Add impulse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.24,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Changes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.24,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Add animation and backgrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.24,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Modify program
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:21.24,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Opening!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.65,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this battle started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:31.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to exceed our limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.48,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,It's... done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:43.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Five hours until we open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:49.39,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,In these few remaining hours, we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.64,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get ready for the show by sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.42,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:10.12,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Once the festival's over, Shiina will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.96,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Message Received\NShiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:19.29,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:28.63,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:28.00,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Sending
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.33,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Message Received\NShiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:35.64,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:37.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.68,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:53.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay with \Nme until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:34.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get \Nnervous about Nyapollon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:41.08,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)}#12 The Power of Love in the Culture Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:37.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They say to eat three people, \Nright? Om nom nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:38.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,These lame jokes just aren't me!
